    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver despite showing its age. The engine runs and the car is drivable, though you may notice some minor mechanical quirks and typical wear on the suspension over time. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading in the paint, while the interior shows clear signs of use, including some staining on the upholstery and wear on the dashboard controls. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
