    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a practical choice for someone needing reliable transportation. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings consistent with its age, and the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car starts and drives well, though it may require minor maintenance soon to keep it in top shape. It is a solid, honest car for anyone looking for a budget-friendly daily driver.",
